    private String text;

    public String getMimeType() {
        return mimeType;
    }

    public void setMimeType(String mimeType) {
        this.mimeType = mimeType;
    }

<fim_suffix>    public List<HarPostDataParam> getParams() {

    }

        this.params = params;
    }

        return text;
    }

    public void setText(String text) {
        this.text = text;
    }
